_________________________
CHECKOUT AND DEVENV SETUP

Prerequisites
- JDK 1.6.0
- Eclipse SDK >= 3.5.0
- Apache Maven >= 3.0.3 
- Python >= 2.7 (to make releases only)

In Eclipse checkout:
- https://svn.codespot.com/a/eclipselabs.org/wsprefs-transferrer/trunk/org.eclipselabs.wsprefs.transferrer.ui
- https://svn.codespot.com/a/eclipselabs.org/wsprefs-transferrer/trunk/org.eclipselabs.wsprefs.transferrer.feature
- https://svn.codespot.com/a/eclipselabs.org/wsprefs-transferrer/trunk/org.eclipselabs.wsprefs.transferrer.updatesite


______________
RELEASE HOW TO

- Checkout
  - checkout https://svn.codespot.com/a/eclipselabs.org/wsprefs-transferrer/releases ($RELDIR)
  - adapt repository config in parent pom if necessary
  - checkout https://svn.codespot.com/a/eclipselabs.org/wsprefs-transferrer/updatesite ($SITEDIR)

- Disable CI Build

- OSGi version hacking
  - run prepare_rel.py
  - commit

- Release
  - checkout https://svn.codespot.com/a/eclipselabs.org/wsprefs-transferrer
  - cd wsprefs-transferrer
  - mvn release:prepare release:perform -Dusername=googleUser -Dpassword=googleSvnPassword
  - commit all changes in $RELDIR
  - remove all files from $SITEDIR
  - unzip $RELDIR/org/eclipselabs/wsprefs/transferrer/org.eclipselabs.wsprefs.transferrer.updatesite/$VERSION/\
    org.eclipselabs.wsprefs.transferrer.updatesite-$VERSION-site.zip to $SITEDIR
  - commit all changes in $SITEDIR

- More OSGi version hacking
  - run prepare_dev.py
  - commit

- Enable CI build

- Test installation from https://svn.codespot.com/a/eclipselabs.org/wsprefs-transferrer/updatesite

- Update version in Eclipse Marketplace 